I set the video with the hubl to autoplay and then I use the videoAPI to start and stop the video, Iâ€™m still working on this, but the basic js is something like

```window.addEventListener('message', (e) =&gt; {
    console.log(e)
    // e.data.embedId is not in accumulatorPauseVideos
    if(e.data.type == "PLAYER_PLAY" &amp;&amp;  !accumulatorPauseVideos.includes(e.data.embedId)) {
        let player = window.hsVideoApi.getPlayer(e.data.embedId)
        player.postMessageToPlayer("SET_PLAYER_STATUS", {status: "PAUSED"})
        accumulatorPauseVideos.push(e.data.embedId)
    }
});```
